*** Install instructions ***

- Copy all files to a folder on a webserver that supports PHP and have route to 
SQL Server host;

- Write permission to files:
   - db.vars.php
   - php-query-analyzer-tables-used-in-selects
   - php-query-analyzer-tempfile-for-csv-export

- Openup index.php on a browser, and edit db vars on configuration link on top menu.

Any problems please feel free to send me a mail... miguel.axcar@gmail.com

Brazilian regards, Luiz "Miguel" Axcar
